titletitlepresidential_patiencetitle: True Sandbox

True Sandbox menu, where you can actually change things around. Be sure to keep in mind, for technical players, there is also option to change variables in "technical work" option -> "set variable" option.

- @fastforward: Skip two weeks
- @budge: Budget and economics
- @relaton: Relationships menu
- @party: Internal party - strength - dissent
- @class_votes: Class popularities of parties
- @dissent: Party dissents
- @advisor: Advisor Action Timer
- @kpd: KPD normalization (50 relation, communist coalition 6)
- @hinden: Hindenburg patience
- @dvpposition: Change DVP orientation
- @dnvpposition: Change DNVP orientation
- @changeddp: Change DDP orientation
- @coup: Launch right coup
- @strike: Launch capital strike
- @generale: Launch general strike
- @forces: Forces
- @bans: Party Ban Statuses
- @kill_me: Set time
- @deterministic: Turn on deterministic mod
- @bypasshistoricalsaves: Historical mode saves removed
- @sandbox.sandbox_menu: Back

@deterministic

- @turn_on_det: Turn Deterministic On
- @turn_off_det: Turn Deterministic ff
- @truesandbox

@turn_on_det
view-if: deterministic_mode = 0
on-arrival: deterministic_mode = 1
go-to: deterministic

@turn_off_det
view-if: deterministic_mode = 1
on-arrival: deterministic_mode = 0
go-to: deterministic

