@hinden

How much?

- @100: By 100+
- @50: By 50+
- @10: By 10+
- @5: By 5+
- @1: By 1+
- @-100: By 100-
- @-50: By 50-
- @-10: By 10-
- @-5: By 5-
- @-1: By 1-
- @truesandbox: Back

@100
on-arrival: presidential_patience += 100; 
go-to: hinden

Done. 100+

@50
on-arrival: presidential_patience += 50; 
go-to: hinden

Done

@10
on-arrival: presidential_patience += 10; 
go-to: hinden

Done

@5
on-arrival: presidential_patience += 5; 
go-to: hinden

Zone

@1
on-arrival: presidential_patience += 1; 
go-to: hinden

Sone

@-100
on-arrival: presidential_patience -= 100; 
go-to: hinden

Hone

@-50
on-arrival: presidential_patience -= 50; 
go-to: hinden

Gone

@-10
on-arrival: presidential_patience -= 10; 
go-to: hinden

Lone

@-5
on-arrival: presidential_patience -= 5; 
go-to: hinden

Bone

@-1
on-arrival: presidential_patience -= 1; 
go-to: hinden

Pone


